"A traditional Finnish plucked string instrument played over the lap. It has "
"a distinctive bell-like sound."
msgstr "一種傳統的芬蘭撥絃樂器，演奏時置於膝上。它具有獨特的鐘鈴般音色。"

#: .\ver_items.json
msgid "egg vibrator"
msgid_plural "egg vibrators"
msgstr[0] "跳蛋"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'egg vibrator', 'str_pl': 'egg vibrators'}
#: .\ver_items.json
msgid ""
"A discreet adult toy perfect for winding down and relaxing. Not as powerful "
"as a regular vibrator, but takes up less space."
msgstr "一款精巧的成人玩具，非常適合放鬆身心。雖不如常規振動器強勁，但更節省空間。"

#: .\ver_items.json
msgid "vintage MRE"
msgid_plural "vintage MREs"
msgstr[0] "老式單兵口糧"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'vintage MRE', 'str_pl': 'vintage MREs'}
#: .\ver_items.json
msgid ""
"A 'Meal Ready to Eat' that was once fresh and just what any soldier needed. "
"It comes with various food things and accessories. Nowadays, it's not "
"looking as hot, but the contents should still be nice! Disassemble to "
"unpack."
msgstr "一種曾經新鮮、能滿足士兵需求的'即食餐'。內含多種食物和配件。如今看起來雖不怎麼樣，但裡面的東西應該還不錯！拆解即可打開。"

#: .\ver_items.json
msgid "vintage beef course"
msgid_plural "vintage beef courses"
msgstr[0] "老式牛肉主菜"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'vintage beef course'}
#: .\ver_items.json
msgid ""
"The now unsealed main course of a vintage MRE. It's not looking incredibly "
"appetizing, but it should still be good eating."
msgstr "一份已開封的老式單兵口糧主菜。看起來不太誘人，但吃起來應該還行。"

#: .\ver_items.json
msgid "canine dildo"
