#. ~ Description for {'str': 'canine dildo', 'str_pl': 'canine dildos'}
#: .\ver_items.json
msgid ""
"Well, this thing's sure obscene. It appears to be quite hefty and "
"anatomically correct, too. If that's your thing, go wild. Pervert."
msgstr "好吧，這東西確實夠下流的。它看起來相當沉重，而且解剖結構也很逼真。如果你就好這口，那就盡情享受吧。變態。"

#: .\ver_items.json
