msgid ""
"Good lord! How depraved can someone get? You suppose you could use it to "
"whack zombies around thanks to its sheer size, if you won't mind it flopping"
" around. Or just use it. Whatever."
msgstr "老天爺！人到底能有多墮落？如果你不介意它晃來晃去，或許可以憑其巨大尺寸用來敲打殭屍。或者就直接用吧。隨便你。"

#: .\ver_magazine.json
