#. ~ Description for {'str': 'high-frequency blade'}
#: .\ver_weapons.json
msgid ""
"A high-tech prototype katana reinforced with a powerful alternating current,"
" causing the blade to resonate at extremely high frequencies. Because of how"
" the oscillation weakens any molecular bond the blade touches, it has little"
" trouble cutting through most anything."
msgstr "一把高科技原型武士刀，由強大的交流電強化，使刀刃以極高頻率共振。由於振盪會削弱刀刃接觸的任何分子鍵，它能輕鬆切割大多數物體。"

#: .\ver_weapons.json
msgid "jet hammer (off)"
msgid_plural "jet hammer (off)s"
msgstr[0] "噴氣錘（關閉）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'jet hammer (off)'}.
#: .\ver_weapons.json
msgid "The jet hammer sputters to life."
msgstr "噴氣錘噼啪啟動。"

#. ~ Use action need_charges_msg for {'str': 'jet hammer (off)'}.
#: .\ver_weapons.json
msgid "Not enough gasoline！"
msgstr "汽油不足！"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'jet hammer (off)'}
#: .\ver_weapons.json
msgid ""
"A large, full-metal sledgehammer that has a pair of tiny thrusters and a "
"small engine attached to the head. Quite unwieldy and unbalanced when it's "
"turned off. Activate to turn on."
msgstr "一把大型全金屬大錘，錘頭裝有一對微型推進器和一個小引擎。關閉時相當笨重且不平衡。激活以開啟。"

