msgstr[0] "絕對收割者"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'Absolute Reaper'}.
#: .\ver_weapons.json
msgid "Reaper's got your name!"
msgstr "收割者已記下你的名字！"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Absolute Reaper'}
#: .\ver_weapons.json
msgid ""
"'Reaper, reaper, that's what people call me. Why? 'Cause they all die. When "
"I sing I end their lives...'"
msgstr "'收割者，收割者，人們都這麼叫我。為什麼？因為他們都會死。當我歌唱時，我終結他們的生命……'"

#: .\ver_weapons.json
